title: Phoenix @ Coachella 2013
description:
Rip of the Phoenix at Coachella 2013 (Indio, USA) Week 1, Day 2.
This video came from the youtube stream of Coachella on Youtube.

It is not a 10/10 quality for the video because the source sux but it's better that nothing.

For others concerts get on this channel.I can't upload on my records because i don't have many upload, so i upload the concert who as ban on youtube for copyright.

It's the only show of Phoenix that you can found on the internet.

Have fun :p
